    # gl "Oh yeah?"
    gl "Ah, sim?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzyp4.rpy:16
translate portuguese izzyp4_c02c2521:

    # pc "Yeah, one of my friends is having to leave her job at Jackson Burger. They're looking for a new waitress."
    pc "Sim, uma das minhas amigas vai ter de deixar o emprego no Jackson Burger. Estão à procura de uma nova empregada de mesa."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzyp4.rpy:18
translate portuguese izzyp4_0b7b081b:

    # gl "A waitress job? Man, that's not really my thing."
    gl "Um emprego de empregada de mesa? Caramba, isso não é bem a minha onda."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzyp4.rpy:20
translate portuguese izzyp4_98a7524a:

    # gl "But at this point, I'll take what I can get."
    gl "Mas, a esta altura, aceito o que vier."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzyp4.rpy:21
translate portuguese izzyp4_9a7e05b5:

    # gl "Did she like the job? Why is she leaving?"
    gl "Ela gostava do emprego? Porque é que vai sair?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzyp4.rpy:22
translate portuguese izzyp4_56c9f3fd:

    # pc "She's starting at a veterinary job soon. She liked the job though, yeah. She said the owner is a really nice guy."
    pc "Ela vai começar a trabalhar numa clínica veterinária em breve. Mas ela gostava do trabalho, sim. Ela disse que o dono é um tipo muito simpático."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzyp4.rpy:23
translate portuguese izzyp4_3d91189b:

    # gl "Alright, I'll try for it."
    gl "Está bem, vou tentar."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzyp4.rpy:24
translate portuguese izzyp4_5573e1d8:

    # pc "Here, I'll give you Mari's number. She'll probably be able to help you."
    pc "Toma, vou dar-te o número da Mari. Ela provavelmente vai poder ajudar-te."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzyp4.rpy:25
translate portuguese izzyp4_3dff977c:

    # gl "Cool."
    gl "Fixe."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzyp4.rpy:26
translate portuguese izzyp4_c56ff175:

    # "I give her Mari's phone number and she puts it in her phone contacts."
    "Dou-lhe o número de telefone da Mari e ela guarda-o nos contactos do telemóvel."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzyp4.rpy:28
translate portuguese izzyp4_ef7a6e14:

    # gl "Thanks, Twig. I appreciate your help. Really."
    gl "Obrigada, Twig. Agradeço a tua ajuda. A sério."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzyp4.rpy:29
translate portuguese izzyp4_c5692f98:

    # pc "No problem. I hope you get the job."
    pc "Não há problema. Espero que consigas o emprego."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzyconversations/izzyp4.rpy:30
translate portuguese izzyp4_e1bc7428:

    # gl "Me too. I'm really starting to struggle for money."
    gl "Eu também. Estou a começar a ter muitas dificuldades financeiras."

translate portuguese strings:

